    <stitle>FRONT NON-DRIVE STEERING AXLE: ROCKWELL - CLEAN AND INSPECT - CLEANING THE GROUND OR POLISHED PARTS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="repair" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CLEANING THE GROUND OR POLISHED PARTS</title>
        <para>Use a cleaning solvent to clean ground or polished parts and surfaces. Kerosene or diesel fuel can be used
            for this purpose.
            <emph type="bold">Do not use gasoline</emph>.
        </para>
        <para>Do
            <emph type="bold">not</emph>
            clean ground or polished parts in a hot solution tank or with water, steam or alkaline solutions. These
            solutions will cause corrosion of the parts.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
